## Box Plot

```{julia;echo=false; fig_cap="Box Plot"; label="bp1"; fig_width=7; fig_height=3}
s = stackedData

boxplot(s,:variable,:value,keys(s.colindex)[2:end],fillalpha=0.3, fillcolor=:orange)
plot!(size=(1000,500))
plot!(grid=false)
plot!(leg=false)
```

## Parallel Bar Chart

```{julia;echo=false; fig_cap="Question Parallel Bar Chart"; label="pbc1"; fig_width=7; fig_height=3}
s = scaledData

bar(s,:variable,keys(s.colindex)[end:-1:2], bar_width=0.7)
plot!(s,:variable,keys(s.colindex)[end:-1:2], linewidth=2, linecolor=:black)
plot!(leg=false)
plot!(xlabel = "Question", ylabel = "Score Percentage")
plot!(size=(1000,500))
plot!(grid=false)
```

